                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " In order to get values of DDX,",
                "polyethylene scatterer of identical size of the sample",
                "was used to measure the total counts for the n-p",
                "scattering peak Nh(25 degr.) at 25 degr. The n-p",
                "scattering neutron counts Nh(25 degr.) were accurately",
                "measured with the statistical uncertainty < 2%."
              ]
            }
          ],
