                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error sources of the data mainly come",
                "from;",
                "  * the counting statistics (about 10%-20% for most of",
                "    energy bins),",
                "  * the background subtraction (about 10%),",
                "  * the efficiency of neutron detector (about 3%)",
                "  * the correction errors of Monte-Carlo calculation,",
                "    which were about 3% for 6,7Li samples and",
